OL,5,G2000 FIFA World Cup 2026
OL,6,     FEngland v Croatia (Kick-off
OL,7,     F9.00pm). Mark Pougatch presents
OL,8,     Fcoverage of the Group L match at
OL,9,     FDallas Stadium in the USA, as
OL,10,     FThomas Tuchel's side get their
OL,11,     Fcampaign under way. These two
OL,12,     Fteams last met at the European
OL,13,     FChampionships held in 2021, with
OL,14,     FEngland winning a group stage
OL,15,     Fencounter 1-0 at Wembley Stadium
OL,16,     Fthanks to a second-half finish
OL,17,     Ffrom Raheem Sterling. They also
OL,18,     Fmet in the semi-finals of the 2018
OL,19,     FWorld Cup in Russia, when Croatia
OL,20,     Fcame from behind to win 2-1 in
OL,21,     Fextra-time and reach their first
OL,22,     Fmajor final. Kieran Trippier
OL,23,Vppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
