OL,5,G2340 FIFA World Cup 2026
OL,6,     FGhana v Panama (Kick-off 12.00am).
OL,7,     FMark Pougatch presents coverage of
OL,8,     Fthe Group L match at Toronto
OL,9,     FStadium in Canada, as these two
OL,10,     Fsides get their tournaments under
OL,11,     Fway in their first-ever meeting.
OL,12,     FGhana made it through to the
OL,13,     Ffinals after finishing top of CAF
OL,14,     Fqualifying Group I, above the
OL,15,     Flikes of Madagascar, Mali and
OL,16,     FComoros after winning eight of
OL,17,     Ftheir 10 matches. This is their
OL,18,     Ffifth appearance at the World Cup
OL,19,     Ffinals and their second successive
OL,20,     Ftournament after taking part four
OL,21,     Fyears ago in Qatar. Their
OL,22,     Fopponents tonight also finished
