OL,5,G0530 James Martin's American Adventure
OL,6,     FThe travelling chef ventures into
OL,7,     FLouisiana's state capital Baton
OL,8,     FRouge to experience a unique
OL,9,     FAmerican phenomenon - tailgating.
OL,10,     FIt's the day of a big football
OL,11,     Fmatch at Louisiana State
OL,12,     FUniversity, and the LSU Tigers are
OL,13,     Fplaying in front of thousands of
OL,14,     Ffans. Surrounded by people
OL,15,     Fbarbecuing, cooking and sharing
OL,16,     Ffood from the back of their
OL,17,     Fpick-up trucks, James joins in and
OL,18,     Fcooks up a storm ahead of the
OL,19,     Fgame. He also takes time out to
OL,20,     Fvisit a Baton Rouge-based oyster
OL,21,     Frestaurant specialising in North
OL,22,     FAmerican varieties
